### Attack Simulation Commands

The following commands were used to generate malicious traffic and test detection capabilities of Suricata IDS.

## 1. Nmap Port Scan
   
   * nmap TARGET_IP

## 2. Aggressive Scan

   * nmap -A TARGET_IP

## 3. SYN Stealth Scan

   * nmap -sS TARGET_IP

## 4. Ping Flood

   * ping -f TARGET_IP

## 5. SSH Brute Force

  * hydra -l ubuntu -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt TARGET_IP ssh

## 6. FTP Brute Force

  * hydra -l ftpuser -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt TARGET_IP ftp

## 7. DNS Request

  * nslookup google.com

## 8. DNS Query

  * dig github.com

## 9. HTTP Request

   * curl http://TARGET_IP

## 10. Network Discovery

   * netdiscover -r NETWORK_RANGE

